text: Jack Bannon (born 24 March 1991) is an English actor. He is known for his role as Christopher Morcom in The Imitation Game, as Sam Thursday on the ITV drama series Endeavour (2013-2018, 2023) and as Alfred Pennyworth on the Epix crime drama series Pennyworth (2019â€“2022).
